## oh-my-pi (MIT)

Veyyon is a source fork of oh-my-pi (`can1357/oh-my-pi`), MIT licensed. The
bulk of the TypeScript/Bun agent loop and TUI, the `pi-*` Rust natives (grep,
PTY, hashline edits), provider integrations, and session/role plumbing carry
forward from it. The MIT permission notice for that incorporated code is the
root `LICENSE` in this repository.

